<koken:include file="includes/header.html" />
    <section id="about-me" class="hidden-phone">
        <div class="wrapper">
            <div id="services">
                <h2>Services</h2>
                <p>I build web sites that look great on devices big or small using HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript along with other technologies. Web development is a two-way conversation between the developer and the client. I'll work with you to make sure your users are having the best experience current technology can deliver.</p>

                <p>I'll start with either some sketches or wireframe mock-ups of your design&hellip; maybe both. Then, depending on the site, I'll either move on to a high-fidelity mockup in something like Photoshop, or I'll start building a working prototype in real HTML. You'll be in the loop every step of the way.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="wrapper">
            <div id="skills">
                <h2>Skills</h2>
                <div class="set">
                    <h3>Front-end web development</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>HTML5</li>
                        <li>CSS3, SASS, &amp; LESS</li>
                        <li>JavaScript &amp; jQuery</li>
                        <li>Email template design</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="set">
                    <h3>Back-end web development</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Python</li>
                        <li>webapp2</li>
                        <li>Django</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="set">
                    <h3>Others</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Copywriting</li>
                        <li>Managing email campaigns with MailChimp</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <h2 id="featured-heading" class="h1">Featured Projects</h2>
    <p id="featured-intro">Below, you'll find some of my best recent work. Check out <a href="http://raddevon.dunked.com/" target="_blank">my comprehensive portfolio</a> to see the rest.</p>
    <section id="projects">
        <koken:load source="featured_albums">
            <koken:loop>
                <div class="project-wrap">
                    <div class="project-image">
                        <koken:link>
                            <koken:img respond_to="width" lazy="true" fade="200" />
                        </koken:link>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text">
                        <h2>
                            <koken:link>
                                {{ album.title }}
                            </koken:link>
                        </h2>
                        <p>{{ album.description }}</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </koken:loop>
        <koken:else>
            <koken:note>
                <p>This page displays featured albums. Assign some in the library.</p>
            </koken:note>
        </koken:load>
    </section>
    <div id="contact">
        <div class="typeform-widget" data-url="http://raddevon.typeform.com/to/LlghO7" data-text="What can I build for you? Tap to contact me."></div>
